From 6bfaaa6f54030f76be2d6ab952741466021564f9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: William Escande <wescande@google.com>
Date: Fri, 27 Feb 2026 14:20:29 -0800
Subject: [PATCH] Add support for default values in sysprop definitions.

This change introduces a "default_value" field in the sysprop proto.
When a property is defined with a "default_value", the generated APIs will return the specified default value if the system property
is not set or is empty. The return type of the generated getter
functions is also adjusted to be non-optional when a default value is
provided.

Bug: 269635186
Test: atest sysprop_test
Change-Id: I495c8e2e15baacf1eb18d4cacb439a8196cd1569
---
 CppGen.cpp                 |  60 ++-
 JavaGen.cpp                |  23 +-
 RustGen.cpp                |  53 ++-
 sysprop.proto              |   1 +
 tests/CppGenTest.cpp       |   5 +-
 tests/DefaultValueTest.cpp | 724 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 6 files changed, 842 insertions(+), 24 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 tests/DefaultValueTest.cpp

